articles.title: A shark kills a woman and seriously wounds another swimmer at an Australian beach - AP News
articles.description: Authorities say a shark killed a woman and seriously wounded another swimmer at an Australian national park. The attack occurred early Thursday at Crowdy Bay National Park, which is known for camping, fishing and hiking over 200 miles north of Sydney. Police …
articles.content:
MELBOURNE, Australia (AP) A shark killed a woman and seriously wounded a man taking an early morning swim with her at a national park beach on Australias east coast Thursday, police said.
